YGGDRASIL ETHICAL USE ADDENDUM

Users of this Software agree to:

1. NOT use YGGDRASIL to deliberately spread misinformation or propaganda
2. NOT use YGGDRASIL to harm, manipulate, or deceive individuals or groups
3. NOT use YGGDRASIL to circumvent its truth-verification mechanisms
4. REPORT any vulnerabilities in the truth-verification system responsibly

This addendum is not legally binding but represents the ethical expectations
of the YGGDRASIL community. Violations may result in exclusion from the
community and public disclosure.

